; wavmix32.def — module-definition file for the WAVMIX32.DLL import library.
;
; Authored for this project. Contains only the interface (the DLL name + the exported function
; names the demo imports) — facts, not copyrightable expression. LIB.EXE turns it into
; wavmix32.lib, whose stdcall-decorated symbols (_WaveMix*@N) resolve our objects and import the
; undecorated names from WAVMIX32.DLL by name, exactly like the original binary. A real (or the
; stub) WAVMIX32.DLL provides sound at runtime.
LIBRARY   WAVMIX32
EXPORTS
    WaveMixInit         @1
    WaveMixActivate     @2
    WaveMixOpenWave     @3
    WaveMixOpenChannel  @4
    WaveMixPlay         @5
    WaveMixFlushChannel @6
    WaveMixCloseChannel @7
    WaveMixFreeWave     @8
    WaveMixCloseSession @9
    WaveMixPump         @10
